OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1776780668
OL,3,CReform and Conservatives accused of
OL,4,C'stoking fear' around immigration
OL,6,FBoth the leaders of Reform in Wales
OL,7,Fand the Welsh Conservatives have been
OL,8,Faccused of "stoking fear" and using
OL,9,Fdivisive language when talking about
OL,10,Fimmigration.
OL,12,FWales' political leaders clashed over
OL,13,Fimmigration among other topics as they
OL,14,Ffaced each other in a live debate on
OL,15,FITV Cymru Wales.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/17
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1776780668
OL,3,CReform and Conservatives accused of
OL,4,C'stoking fear' around immigration
OL,6,FThere were a number of fiery exchanges
OL,7,Fthroughout the programme but
OL,8,Fimmigration was the topic which
OL,9,Fgarnered perhaps the most heated
OL,10,Fdebate. ITV Cymru Wales' latest poll
OL,11,Fshowed that tackling immigration is
OL,12,Fthe third biggest priority for voters.
OL,14,FNone of the leaders taking part in the
OL,15,Fdebate will have control over
OL,16,Fimmigration - that remains in the
OL,17,Fpower of the UK Government at
OL,18,FWestminster.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/17
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1776780668
OL,3,CReform and Conservatives accused of
OL,4,C'stoking fear' around immigration
OL,6,FHowever the leaders were asked their
OL,7,Fparty's position on immigration and
OL,8,Fspecifically on the Labour Welsh
OL,9,FGovernment's resettling policy on
OL,10,Fmaking Wales a 'Nation of Sanctuary'.
OL,11,FThe Nation of Sanctuary has cost #68m
OL,12,Fsince it started, with 90% of this
OL,13,Fsupporting Ukrainians.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/17
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1776780668
OL,3,CReform and Conservatives accused of
OL,4,C'stoking fear' around immigration
OL,6,FReform's Dan Thomas laid out his
OL,7,Fparty's view, saying that the policy
OL,8,Fwas done "by stealth" in Wales and
OL,9,Fthat there was "no fairness'. Jane
OL,10,FDodds, Leader of the Welsh Liberal
OL,11,FDemocrats, interrupted to challenge
OL,12,Fhim on the percentage of people living
OL,13,Fin Wales who were born elsewhere.
OL,15,FShe interjected: "Do you know that?
OL,16,F6.9% according to the office of
OL,17,Fimmigration are born outside of the UK.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/17
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1776780668
OL,3,CReform and Conservatives accused of
OL,4,C'stoking fear' around immigration
OL,6,F"Your party is stoking division, you
OL,7,Fare stoking hatred, you are stoking
OL,8,Ffear you should be ashamed of
OL,9,Fyourself."
OL,11,FDan Thomas rebuffed these claims
OL,12,Fsaying: "We are not stoking division,
OL,13,Fnobody is trying to scare anyone.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/17
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1776780668
OL,3,CReform and Conservatives accused of
OL,4,C'stoking fear' around immigration
OL,6,F"This is the problem with the
OL,7,Fimmigration debate. We want to have a
OL,8,Fsensible rational debate about
OL,9,Fimmigration. And we know it is low in
OL,10,FWales at the moment, we want to keep
OL,11,Fit that way because we have seen
OL,12,Fwhat's happened in England and in
OL,13,FEnglish cities and we don't want
OL,14,FCardiff or Wales to turn into that."
OL,16,FAnother fiery moment came when Rhun ap
OL,17,FIorwerth was questioned on Plaid
OL,18,FCymru's policy to devolve powers over
OL,19,Fmigration to Wales should they be
OL,20,Felected.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/17
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1776780668
OL,3,CReform and Conservatives accused of
OL,4,C'stoking fear' around immigration
OL,6,FRhun started his pledge on this topic
OL,7,Fby saying: "We need more students from
OL,8,Fabroad coming to our universities for
OL,9,Fexample and we don't have those powers
OL,10,Fover visas.
OL,12,F"I think it would be a good idea for
OL,13,Fthe future of our universities and our
OL,14,Ffuture economy to bring more people
OL,15,Fin. That's the kind of system we want."
OL,17,FHe said he would look to adopt a sub-
OL,18,Fstate visa model similar system to
OL,19,FCanada.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/17
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1776780668
OL,3,CReform and Conservatives accused of
OL,4,C'stoking fear' around immigration
OL,6,FHe went on to say: "The problem that
OL,7,Fwe have with housing is not the people
OL,8,Fcoming in it is the lack of social
OL,9,Fhousing, the lack of houses being
OL,10,Fbuilt.
OL,12,F"It's the same within the NHS. People
OL,13,Ftell me the NHS's problems are because
OL,14,Fof immigration, they're not. We would
OL,15,Fbe stuck without workers from
OL,16,Felsewhere working within our NHS.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/17
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1776780668
OL,3,CReform and Conservatives accused of
OL,4,C'stoking fear' around immigration
OL,6,F"But let me tell you this, Reform have
OL,7,Fmade it their business to stoke
OL,8,Fdivisive rhetoric over immigration, it
OL,9,Fwas roundly rejected in Caerphilly and
OL,10,Fit's our job to make sure it is
OL,11,Froundly rejected Wales-wide."
OL,13,FDan Thomas was then asked to respond
OL,14,Fto that, to which he said: "We're just
OL,15,Fvoicing the genuine concerns that the
OL,16,Fgeneral public have in Wales about
OL,17,Fimmigration. It's a top three issue
OL,18,Ffor a reason. Reform is the only party
OL,19,Freflecting that concern."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/17
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1776780668
OL,3,CReform and Conservatives accused of
OL,4,C'stoking fear' around immigration
OL,6,FEluned Morgan challenged Dan Thomas on
OL,7,Fthe number of asylum seekers who are
OL,8,Fcurrently housed in hotels in Wales,
OL,9,Fwhich stands at 74.
OL,11,FShe said: "Let's not raise concerns
OL,12,Fwhere there shouldn't be."
OL,14,FReform's Welsh Leader insisted the
OL,15,Fmoney spent on the Nation of Sanctuary
OL,16,Fcould be spent "on Welsh nurses and
OL,17,FWelsh hospital beds".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/17
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1776780668
OL,3,CReform and Conservatives accused of
OL,4,C'stoking fear' around immigration
OL,6,FMs Morgan replied: "Blaming immigrants
OL,7,Fwon't fix the NHS, it won't build
OL,8,Fanymore homes. What you need is
OL,9,Fserious leadership and compassion."
OL,11,FPresenter Adrian Masters then asked
OL,12,Ffor Darren Millar's response saying
OL,13,Fthat similar criticisms had been
OL,14,Fdirected at his party in the past and
OL,15,Fwhether the language used in his party
OL,16,Fhad stoked up the debate.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/17
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1776780668
OL,3,CReform and Conservatives accused of
OL,4,C'stoking fear' around immigration
OL,6,FHe said: "The Welsh Government gets a
OL,7,Fblock grant to spend on the issues for
OL,8,Fwhich it is responsible, and
OL,9,Fimmigration is not a responsibility of
OL,10,Fthe Welsh Government.
OL,12,F"I want to see every pound of that
OL,13,FNation of Sanctuary money invested
OL,14,Finstead in our public services.
OL,16,F"Wales is a nation which has offered
OL,17,Fpeople a home when they are fleeing
OL,18,Fpersecution, fleeing war and that's
OL,19,Fabsolutely right but we also know
OL,20,Fthere are many people making bogus
OL,21,Fasylum claims.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/17
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1776780668
OL,3,CReform and Conservatives accused of
OL,4,C'stoking fear' around immigration
OL,6,F"What I don't accept is the nonsense
OL,7,Fthat we've heard from the Plaid Cymru
OL,8,Fleader in the past when he said
OL,9,Fthere's no such thing as illegal
OL,10,Fimmigration. Of course there is,
OL,11,Fpeople are arriving on British shores
OL,12,Fillegally."
OL,14,FMr Iorwerth responded: "People
OL,15,Fsmuggling is illegal, outstaying visas
OL,16,Fis illegal. People aren't illegal
OL,17,FDarren."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G13/17
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
