PN,46614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1776780668
OL,3,CReform and Conservatives accused of
OL,4,C'stoking fear' around immigration
OL,6,FAnthony Slaughter added: "Immigration
OL,7,Fis high on the list of concerns,
OL,8,Fpeople are talking about it and that's
OL,9,Fbecause your two parties (Reform and
OL,10,FConservatives) keep stoking hatred and
OL,11,Fdivision by exaggerating it.
OL,13,F"You're taking people's anger and
OL,14,Fdespair - anger which they have every
OL,15,Fright to feel with the situation - and
OL,16,Fyou're directing it at other people,
OL,17,Fsome of the most vulnerable people on
OL,18,Fthis planet. You both should be
OL,19,Fashamed of yourself."
OL,26,@qD@ZpmrD@Npn
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G14/17
