CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1776780668
OL,3,CReform and Conservatives accused of
OL,4,C'stoking fear' around immigration
OL,6,FEluned Morgan was asked whether the
OL,7,FNation of Sanctuary policy, enacted by
OL,8,Fthe Welsh Labour Government, was
OL,9,Fvirtue-signalling.
OL,11,FShe defended the policy saying: "I'm
OL,12,Fnot going to apologise for the fact
OL,13,Fthat 91% of that money is spent on
OL,14,Fsettling Ukrainians who are fleeing a
OL,15,Fwar."
OL,17,FShe added: "The NHS is held up by
OL,18,Fpeople from other countries, that's
OL,19,Fsomething we should celebrate."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G15/17
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
