PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1776780668
OL,3,CReform and Conservatives accused of
OL,4,C'stoking fear' around immigration
OL,6,FJane Dodds said she "absolutely"
OL,7,Fsupports the Nation of Sanctuary
OL,8,Fpolicy.
OL,10,FShe said: "I believe Wales is a
OL,11,Fwelcoming country, that's our badge of
OL,12,Fhonour and you can't do that down. And
OL,13,Fyou try all the time, you find a way
OL,14,Fof doing down the Welsh people both
OL,15,FConservatives and Reform and I don't
OL,16,Fthink they are like that".
OL,18,FYou can read a breakdown on each of
OL,19,Fthe leaders' policies on a variety of
OL,20,Fkey topics here or watch the full
OL,21,Fdebate here on ITVX or on Youtube.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G16/17
